author: USA TODAY, Adrianna Rodriguez, USA TODAY
title: What we know about coronavirus keeps changing. Here's all the things you may have missed.
description: Here's a running list of things that have changed the coronavirus and the illness it causes, COVID-19, since it was discovered late last year.
content:
